Bursting with tropical fruits and citrus aromatics and flavours this beer has been brewed for those times when, just like that sneaky Feral fox, one of our Brewpubs chickens just isn’t enough.

items.badge_description: Guess what? We’re officially 14! From October 22nd to October 27th, we’re celebrating Untappd’s 14th anniversary (woo woo)! Thanks to every one of you for making this beautifully diverse community what it is today! Let’s raise our glasses, check in a brew, earn this badge, and cheers to the next 14 years of memories with you! For extra credit, be sure to check out the latest Hop Culture piece on the beers with most 5-star check-ins on Untappd so far in 2024.

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 20 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 5!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 25 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 6!
Traveling the world is hard, but not for you. It's as easy as cracking open a new brew! You have had a beer from at least 15 different regions around the world. Try 5 more for Level 4!
